{"tid":775381,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"明明pizza同菠蘿就好撚夾","createTime":"2018-08-11T06:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T19:28:48.000Z","uid":60219,"like":104,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"161a9f0294bd8e55749fd4c371aceb73da76549b","tid":775381,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"酸酸甜甜，惹味到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580a4a71589544d5fb2f465aa9d8f79302edfb1f","tid":775381,"uid":198583,"like":9,"dislike":23,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:21:54.000Z","msg":"Pineapple will only ruin the look and the taste of a pizza<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccae894c1920de7689298047be8cb3d0d06ec79f","tid":775381,"uid":60219,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"580a4a71589544d5fb2f465aa9d8f79302edfb1f","tid":775381,"uid":198583,"like":9,"dislike":23,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:21:54.000Z","msg":"Pineapple will only ruin the look and the taste of a pizza<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:22:55.000Z","msg":"In a final effort to come to a conclusion, we went to Scott Weiner of&nbsp;Scott&rsquo;s Pizza Tours,&nbsp;an expert on the topic of pizza, who left us with these words of pizza wisdom.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;To those who say pineapple isn&rsquo;t an acceptable pizza topping because it&rsquo;s not Italian &hellip; it existed in Italian food culture long before pepperoni ever did, but nobody complains about that. So many of the popular toppings we argue about are not Italian. Corn on pizza? Buffalo chicken on pizza? Ranch dressing on pizza? Not nearly as much noise about those, <span style=\"color: red;\">but they&rsquo;re absolutely not Italian items and when they&rsquo;re treated right, they taste great.</span><br />\n<br />\n&quot;To those who say pineapple isn&rsquo;t an acceptable pizza topping because it doesn&rsquo;t taste good,&nbsp;they probably haven&rsquo;t had it done right. Raw chunks of pineapple thrown around a pizza? No way. Roasted and pulled pineapple with a honey glaze paired with a fatty pork is delicious. No need for tomato on that pineapple pizza, there&rsquo;s enough acid to go around.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;I am absolutely pro-pineapple and I think about it the same way I think about most food arguments. If you don&rsquo;t like it, don&rsquo;t eat it.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"fe54f9916f2f701fffc18ec9b0486672fca0814e","tid":775381,"uid":2419,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:31:06.000Z","msg":"好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最多話佢唔正宗姐 口味既野邊有得講"},{"pid":"2ee33967031f71074dbef7486dca7c04f140554a","tid":775381,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:26:56.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d8cdd8a2ec88284cb65e46f4ab60dd74d006be6","tid":775381,"uid":26689,"like":10,"dislike":29,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:34:40.000Z","msg":"Pizza落菠蘿  就好似鹹肉粽落生果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29e4807fc81fc3db158c6707a252d034606d156","tid":775381,"uid":60219,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"2d8cdd8a2ec88284cb65e46f4ab60dd74d006be6","tid":775381,"uid":26689,"like":10,"dislike":29,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:34:40.000Z","msg":"Pizza落菠蘿  就好似鹹肉粽落生果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:42:02.000Z","msg":"你個類比都九唔搭八嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\npizza落菠蘿咪同生果撻無分別"},{"pid":"8b11452ae6bd8c0c90edab59cf0b7b810b560a12","tid":775381,"uid":25653,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/0